 on multidimensional problems shows\nimprovements on the preservation of vortex like solutions with important error\nreductions, despite of the fact that no genuine 2D balancing criterion is\nembedded.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Dec 2022 18:11:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 23 Dec 2022 08:12:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-26"}
