 movement of method\nto suitable classes. We evaluate our approach on two publicly available\ndatasets. The results show that our approach outperforms three state-of-the-art\nrefactoring tools including PathMove, JDeodorant, and JMove in effectiveness\nand usefulness. The results also unveil useful findings and provide new\ninsights that benefit other types of feature envy refactoring techniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Dec 2022 08:25:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-26"}
