ve collimators of previous space detectors. In this paper, we\nwill present the LEM geometry, its detection concept, and the results from the\ndeveloped GEANT4 simulation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Dec 2022 14:07:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-26"}
